ion"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/az5gww35/pic_9/' target='_blank'><img alt="秋装备起来  阿迪达斯男子梭织外套EH3748" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202008/16/5f388d9004799450.jpg_e680.jpg" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">隐形拉链打开，里面是很大一个口袋，不仅仅是装饰哦</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/az5gww35/pic_10/' target='_blank'><img alt="秋装备起来  阿迪达斯男子梭织外套EH3748" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202008/16/5f388d90c7a863173.jpg_e680.jpg" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">同样衣服的两侧也都有隐形口袋</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/az5gww35/pic_11/' target='_blank'><img alt="秋装备起来  阿迪达斯男子梭织外套EH3748" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202008/16/5f388d9157d0f9695.jpg_e680.jpg" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">里面的口袋也很大</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/az5gww35/pic_12/' target='_blank'><img alt="秋装备起来  阿迪达斯男子梭织外套EH3748" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202008/16/5f388dc106d575108.jpg_e680.jpg" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">一侧袖子上印有阿迪logo，不算明显</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/az5gww35/pic_13/' target='_blank'><img alt="秋装备起来  阿迪达斯男子梭织外套EH3748" src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202008/16/5f388dc15cd8f8138.jpg_e680.jpg" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">袖口是松紧的</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/az5gww35/pic_14/' target='_blank'><img alt="秋装备起来  阿迪达斯男子梭织外套EH3748" src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202008/16/5f388dc53257a4032.jpg_e680.jpg" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">下摆也是收口的</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/az5gww35/pic_15/' target='_blank'><img alt="秋装备起来  阿迪达斯男子梭织外套EH3748" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202008/16/5f388dc60fd588441.jpg_e680.jpg" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">衣服的面料比较厚实，也比较平整，把拉锁拉开穿起来也够有型</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/az5gww35/pic_16/' target='_blank'><img alt="秋装备起来  阿迪达斯男子梭织外套EH3748" src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202008/16/5f388dcfed4e15150.jpg_e680.jpg" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">后背处9也有口袋的设计</